data.description: Are you looking for a beautiful log-home ranch near Lake Tenkiller? Nestled amidst 17 pristine acres of natural beauty, this extraordinary property unveils a tranquil retreat where serenity and charm unite in perfect harmony, complete with a shop, storage building, and dog kennel. Step inside this charming 1476 SF (CH) home with kitchen island, featuring 3 bed/2 bath home with a large living room with a woodstove. You'll be impressed by the soaring vaulted ceiling and the antler style chandelier and custom light fixtures. An open floor plan perfect for entertaining or just relaxing. The wraparound covered deck is delightful for enjoying the beautiful views of the surrounding hills and countryside. Tucked back in off Indian Rd, you will be awed by the private feeling of being to yourself. It's definitely a 'Must See!'
